name: Token Engineering Commons
additional_notices: Kindly be aware of liquidity-related risks. This notice is not directed at any project in particular, and is more of a cautionary reminder.

description.en: The Token Engineering Commons will enable the creation of ethical, safe, resilient and diverse economic systems to benefit societies around the world. Through funding research, development and education proposals, we want to advance token engineering as an emerging discipline.
